        """Stop accepting new jobs and (optionally) wait for all workers to exit."""
        # Bug 3 fix: send one sentinel per worker so every thread reaches its
        # exit condition. Sentinels use priority 6 (> any real job's 1–5) so they
        # are dequeued only after all pending work drains — graceful shutdown.
